<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Palette"</Bold> helps to apply palette for ChartArea.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Explode All"</Bold> helps to explode all the segments in the pie </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Explode Index"</Bold> helps to select a segment to be exploded</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Explode Radius"</Bold> helps to select the radius of an exploded segment</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Visible"</Bold> sets the visibility of DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"HorizontalAlignment"</Bold> helps to choose the position of DataLabels horizontally. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"VerticalAlignment"</Bold> helps to choose the position of DataLabels vertically. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>

